TextEng: "I want to ask you some questions."
"Can you tell me about this town?"
"How did all you winged elves end up down here?"
Text: "날개 달린 엘프들이 어떻게 여기까지 오게 됐어?"

TextEng: "Speaking to a medusa? That's a neat trick."
"Don't worry. Things will get better, someday."
"You're better off without that snake-haired freak."
Text: "그 뱀머리 괴물 없는 게 더 나아."

TextEng: "Hey, I'm glad she's dead. In fact, I'd kill her again if I got the chance."
Text: "어이, 그녀가 죽어서 기뻐. 사실 기회만 있으면 다시 죽이고 싶어."

TextEng: "I'm sorry. This must be painful for you."
"I go where I want, when I want!"
Text: "난 내가 원할 때 원하는 곳에 가!"

TextEng: "I'm going in there, one way or another."
